    "text": "Princess Toadstool's \nCastle Ahead!\nWe want to extend a \nwarm welcome to Mario\nand his crew! As\nfor Bowser, GO HOME!\nYou'll initially start \nin Standard Mode. You \ncan access all 3 modes\nby pressing SELECT. \nIn Standard Mode, the\nbasic controls are:\n: Jump\nHold  as Yoshi: \nFlutter kick\n: Crouch\n\n\n: Swallow items, \npick up items, or punch\ndepending on which \ncharacter you are. \n\n\nPress  again while \nholding something to \nspit it out or throw it.\n: Hold it down while\nmoving to dash."
